text: Mimenicodes subunicolor is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1973. It is known from New Caledonia.BioLib.cz - Mimenicodes subunicolor. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1973
title: Mimenicodes subunicolor
